&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
</pre><p>
or
</p>
<pre class="wiki">&lt;p&gt;some text&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
</pre><p>
However most new browsers would disregard improperly used &lt;br&gt; and not show them as white space anyways.
